    <item>
      <title>美联储降低风险偏好后，比特币从历史高位回落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/bitcoin-retreats-from-record-high-after-fed-cools-risk-appetite</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储官员表示，对于继续降低借贷成本的速度应更加谨慎，比特币四天来首次下跌，金融市场的投机性押注出现减少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/bitcoin-retreats-from-record-high-after-fed-cools-risk-appetite</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 20:10:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
